snippet.title: Sean Combs: The Reckoning | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Who is the real Sean Combs? In a new four-part documentary by Emmy and Grammy Award–winning executive producer Curtis “50 Cent” Jackson and Emmy Award-winning director Alexandria Stapleton, Sean Combs: The Reckoning is a staggering examination of the media mogul, music legend, and convicted offender. Through explosive, never-before-seen materials, including exclusive interviews with those formerly in his orbit, this documentary tells the story of a powerful, enterprising man and the gilded empire he built — and the underworld that lay just beneath its surface.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81906781

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Sean Combs: The Reckoning | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

This documentary series unpacks the shocking allegations behind Sean "Diddy" Combs and his Bad Boy empire, spanning decades of his life and career.

snippet.title: Tetris® 99 – 50th MAXIMUS CUP Gameplay Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The Tetris® 99 50th MAXIMUS CUP event runs from 11 p.m. PT on December 4 to 10:59 p.m. PT on December 8. To participate, you’ll need to be a Nintendo Switch Online member* and play the Tetris 99 online mode during the event period. You’ll earn event points based on your placement in each match. Once you’ve accumulated a total of 100 event points, a new theme will unlock, featuring art, music and Tetrimino designs inspired by the Kirby Air Riders game that is exclusive to the Nintendo Switch 2 system!

*Nintendo Switch Online membership (sold separately) and Nintendo Account required for online features. This game includes an in-game purchase option for users who do not have a membership. snippet.title: English Stream B | StarLadder Budapest Major 2025 - Stage 2 - Day 3
snippet.description:
Stage 2 of StarLadder CS2 Budapest Major 2025 Stream B is here to deliver next epic battles!
The road to Stage 3 continue here. 8 survivors and 8 invited teams in a Swiss system where every map can end a run or launch one. Watch world-class talent like karrigan, broky, r1nkle, xKacpersky, headtr1ck, npl, KRiMZ, fEAR, VINI, chelo, Swisher, HexT, INS, and jks fighting it out LIVE from Budapest.

The teams will adapt in real time as they clutch and ace to voctiry through tense matchups to lock in a Stage 3 spot.
Who advances? Who falls?
